Package: samplingTools
Type: Package
Title: Functions to create and analyze complex sampling data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Adam", "Maier", email = "adam.maier@tntp.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Adam Maier <adam.maier@tntp.org>
Description: The samplingTools package provides a suite of functions to
    organize data for multistage complex sampling (e.g., serpentine sorting)
    and to help create replicate weights and variance estimates for given
    such designs.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 0.7.6),
    rlang (>= 0.2.1)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
